{"tid":1574302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人帶一包梳打粉發夢（代友出post)","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T07:00:12.000Z","uid":204246,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1c653352899ab5c4b37a9881d8de59cd2348c7","tid":1574302,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"梳打粉 實測左兩樣嘢 <br />\n1.梳打水&quot;飽和溶液&quot;狀態比一般純水撲滅速度明顯地快<br />\n<br />\n2.中椒水後有中和能力，椒水油性用水洗只會擴大受傷範圍，現場好難有大量水沖洗嘅情況，用BB沖涼液都需要大量水，梳打粉加水塗身沖再少量水沖走已經可以。 利申：為測試，醃足成日極高濃度飽和溶液淨係少少爆擦<br />\n<br />\n3.(未測試) 有手足指面對水箭龜有機會入左口，因梳打溶液未普及，無人肯用梳打溶液&quot;浪口&quot;, 實質低濃度梳打溶液甚至可以飲落肚&hellip;(味道似傳說焙茶&hellip;)<br />\n<br />\nps. 梳打粉比生理鹽水便宜，開稀可大量製作臨時沖洗用液體，高濃度則可用於快速滅火<br />\n生理鹽水成本貴 液體亦難以大量攜帶 同埋主理一啲傷口性沖洗先係重點，一包梳打粉都係12-15蚊"},{"pid":"2ae069b1c5e74708463b48085c8820381a332959","tid":1574302,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5e483a9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=86c3c7f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.wit